---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Pipeline">

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="overline">Pipeline</p>
      <h1>Making biology programmable for animal health.</h1>
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p>We're innovators. We look for measurable gaps in animal health and build the programmable biologics to close them.</p>
        <p>Every program starts with strain engineering, the foundation of our proprietary platform, and spans infectious disease, sustainability, and chronic disease therapeutics. We apply AI/ML to target selection, accelerate payload and candidate design, and we draw on our proprietary microbiome library to identify high-potential strains as starting points.</p>
        <p>The result: novel veterinary biologics that address important animal health challenges in a safe, sustainable, and economically relevant manner — healthier animals, fewer antibiotics, and new tools for what matters most to protein producers and pet owners.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <Button color="navy" variant="filled" href="/products/be-101">Explore BE-101</Button>
        <Button color="navy" variant="outline" href="/science/our-platform">Explore Our Platform</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ BACKED BY SCIENCE ============ -->
  <!--
    FLAGGED AS UNCERTAIN PER COPY DECK: "This section may not be needed. It is included
    as a placeholder." Also requires Aaron's sign-off before publishing any efficacy
    figures — keep strictly to the published, peer-reviewed result (Hall et al., 2026),
    nothing from internal investor materials. Safe to delete this whole <section> if the
    decision is to cut it.
  -->
  <section class="proof">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Our proof is in our execution.</h2>
      <p>Our lead program, BE-101, has already shown what the BiomEdit platform can do. In controlled trials, engineered strains outperformed both prophylactic antibiotics and wild-type probiotics on feed conversion and weight gain for broiler chickens — with mechanistic evidence behind the result, not just an observed outcome.</p>
      <Button color="navy" variant="outline" href="/science/patents-publications">Read the Research</Button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ PIPELINE SNAPSHOT ============ -->
  <section class="snapshot">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="overline">Pipeline Snapshot</p>
      <h2>Three focus areas. One BiomEdit platform.</h2>
      <div class="snapshot-intro">
        <p>Our programmable veterinary biologics platform spans infectious disease, sustainability, and chronic disease therapeutics. We engineer bacteria to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>deliver nanobodies, peptides, or enzymes (like the strains behind BE-101), or</li>
          <li>work together as a microbial consortium.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>One platform, built to pivot based on what we're solving for.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Both Sustainability color variants shown stacked, pending that decision -->
      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">Sustainability shown in Ember Orange</p>
        <div class="pipeline-example">
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt" id="pt-all" checked>
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt" id="pt-found">
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt" id="pt-invest">
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt" id="pt-break">
          <div class="pipeline-header">
            <div><svg class="pipeline-logo" viewBox="0 0 164 40"><use href="#biomedit-logo" xlink:href="#biomedit-logo"></use></svg><p class="pipeline-title">Our Pipeline</p></div>
            <div class="pipeline-tabs">
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt-all">All</label>
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt-found">Infectious Disease</label>
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt-invest">Chronic Disease</label>
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt-break">Sustainability</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pipeline-columns">
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 1</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Discovery / Design</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-breakthrough"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-117</span><span class="focus">AMR</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Exploratory research into non-antibiotic pathways for resistant-pathogen control, building on lessons from the platform's lead antimicrobial programs.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-breakthrough"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-17</span><span class="focus">Metabolic Disease</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>A next-generation approach to metabolic health, building on early signals from the platform's foundational research.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 2</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Candidate Optimization</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-foundational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-07</span><span class="focus">AMR</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Early trial data testing whether the platform's approach can reduce reliance on antibiotics for resistant-pathogen control.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-investigational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-102</span><span class="focus">Metabolic Disease</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Initial trials evaluating impact on metabolic health markers tied to feed conversion efficiency in production animals.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-investigational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-106</span><span class="focus">Gut Health</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Advancing through pivotal studies to confirm gut health outcomes at the scale required for commercial production settings.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-breakthrough"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-105</span><span class="focus">Methane Reduction</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Tuning a microbiome-based approach to enteric methane reduction in cattle, balancing emissions impact against feed efficiency.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 3</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Proof of Concept</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 4</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Pivotal Studies</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-foundational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-01</span><span class="focus">Gut Health</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Refining strain performance to improve gut barrier integrity and nutrient absorption ahead of formal proof-of-concept trials.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-investigational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-101</span><span class="focus">Pathogen Protection</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>The platform's most advanced candidate, progressing through final regulatory review ahead of commercial launch.</p><a href="/products/be-101" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 5</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Regulatory Approval / Launch Readiness</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-foundational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-02</span><span class="focus">Pathogen Protection</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Early-stage work identifying microbial candidates that can neutralize pathogen-associated toxins before symptoms take hold in the herd or flock.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 6</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Commercial</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">Sustainability shown in Green</p>
        <div class="pipeline-example sustain-green">
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt2" id="pt2-all" checked>
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt2" id="pt2-found">
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt2" id="pt2-invest">
          <input class="tab-input" type="radio" name="tabs-pt2" id="pt2-break">
          <div class="pipeline-header">
            <div><svg class="pipeline-logo" viewBox="0 0 164 40"><use href="#biomedit-logo" xlink:href="#biomedit-logo"></use></svg><p class="pipeline-title">Our Pipeline</p></div>
            <div class="pipeline-tabs">
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt2-all">All</label>
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt2-found">Infectious Disease</label>
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt2-invest">Chronic Disease</label>
              <label class="pipeline-tab" for="pt2-break">Sustainability</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pipeline-columns">
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 1</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Discovery / Design</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-breakthrough"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-117</span><span class="focus">AMR</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Exploratory research into non-antibiotic pathways for resistant-pathogen control, building on lessons from the platform's lead antimicrobial programs.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-breakthrough"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-17</span><span class="focus">Metabolic Disease</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>A next-generation approach to metabolic health, building on early signals from the platform's foundational research.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 2</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Candidate Optimization</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-foundational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-07</span><span class="focus">AMR</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Early trial data testing whether the platform's approach can reduce reliance on antibiotics for resistant-pathogen control.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-investigational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-102</span><span class="focus">Metabolic Disease</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Initial trials evaluating impact on metabolic health markers tied to feed conversion efficiency in production animals.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-investigational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-106</span><span class="focus">Gut Health</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Advancing through pivotal studies to confirm gut health outcomes at the scale required for commercial production settings.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-breakthrough"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-105</span><span class="focus">Methane Reduction</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Tuning a microbiome-based approach to enteric methane reduction in cattle, balancing emissions impact against feed efficiency.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 3</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Proof of Concept</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 4</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Pivotal Studies</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-foundational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-01</span><span class="focus">Gut Health</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Refining strain performance to improve gut barrier integrity and nutrient absorption ahead of formal proof-of-concept trials.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-investigational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-101</span><span class="focus">Pathogen Protection</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>The platform's most advanced candidate, progressing through final regulatory review ahead of commercial launch.</p><a href="/products/be-101" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 5</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Regulatory Approval / Launch Readiness</p>
              <details class="pipeline-card cat-foundational"><summary><div class="card-top-row"><span class="card-main"><span class="code">BE-02</span><span class="focus">Pathogen Protection</span></span><svg class="chevron" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2.5 4.5L6 8L9.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></summary><div class="card-detail"><p>Early-stage work identifying microbial candidates that can neutralize pathogen-associated toxins before symptoms take hold in the herd or flock.</p><a href="/products" class="card-detail-link">Learn more &rarr;</a></div></details>
            </div>
            <div class="pipeline-col">
              <p class="stage-eyebrow">Stage 6</p>
              <p class="pipeline-stage-head">Commercial</p>
