      </div>

      <p class="species-callout">Our programs address the needs of poultry, cattle, swine, dogs, and cats.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ BE-101 SPOTLIGHT ============ -->
  <section class="spotlight">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="spotlight-card">
        <p class="overline">BE-101 · Featured Program</p>
        <h2>BE-101 (Optavant&trade;) is a series of firsts.</h2>
        <ul class="firsts-list">
          <li>First programmable veterinary biologic to reach commercial launch (Q4 2026)</li>
          <li>First engineered microbial therapeutic ever to achieve licensure:
            <ul>
              <li>in any species,</li>
              <li>in any geography,</li>
              <li>in any regulatory path.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <Button color="navy" variant="filled" href="/products/be-101">Learn About BE-101</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ CLOSING CTA BAR ============ -->
  <section class="closing-cta">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Interested in what's next for BiomEdit?</h2>
      <div class="closing-ctas">
        <Button color="navy" variant="filled" href="/science/our-platform">Explore Our Platform</Button>
        <Button color="navy" variant="outline" href="/investors-partners#partner">Partner With Us</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .wrap { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }
  section { padding: 72px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }

  /* ---------- hero ---------- */
  .hero { padding-top: 88px; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 51px); max-width: 780px; margin: 0 0 28px; }
  .hero-copy { max-width: 680px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .hero-copy p { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* ---------- backed by science ---------- */
  .proof { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
  .proof h2 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .proof p { max-width: 680px; margin-bottom: 24px; }

  /* ---------- snapshot ---------- */
  .snapshot h2 { font-size: 28px; margin: 8px 0 24px; }
  .snapshot-intro { max-width: 680px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .snapshot-intro ul { margin: 0 0 16px; padding-left: 20px; }
  .snapshot-intro li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .species-callout {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 32px 0 0;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  /* ---------- BE-101 spotlight ---------- */
  .spotlight { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
  .spotlight-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 48px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }
  .spotlight-card h2 { font-size: 32px; margin: 8px 0 20px; max-width: 640px; }
  .firsts-list { margin: 0 0 28px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 640px; }
  .firsts-list li { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .firsts-list ul { margin-top: 8px; padding-left: 20px; }
  .firsts-list ul li { font-size: 15px; }

  /* ---------- closing CTA bar ---------- */
  .closing-cta { border-bottom: none; text-align: center; }
  .closing-cta h2 { font-size: 28px; margin: 0 0 24px; }
  .closing-ctas { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .wrap { padding: 0 24px; }
    section { padding: 48px 0; }
    .hero { padding-top: 56px; }
    .spotlight-card { padding: 32px 24px; }
  }

  /* ---------- pipeline component (ported from styleguide) ---------- */
  .subsection{margin-bottom:56px;}
  .subsection:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  .sub-label{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-teal);margin:0 0 6px;}
  .pipeline-example{border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg-secondary);}
  .pipeline-header{padding:24px 24px 20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;background:var(--bg-tertiary);}
  .pipeline-title{font-weight:700;font-size:17px;margin:0;color:var(--text-primary);}
  .pipeline-tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .pipeline-logo{width:78px;height:17px;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;}
  input.tab-input{display:none;}
  .pipeline-tab{padding:7px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-secondary);background:var(--bg-secondary);border:1px solid var(--border-color);user-select:none;}
  .pipeline-tab[for$="-found"]{color:var(--color-teal);border-color:var(--color-teal);}
  .pipeline-tab[for$="-invest"]{color:var(--color-navy);border-color:var(--color-navy);}
  .pipeline-tab[for$="-break"]{color:var(--color-orange);border-color:var(--color-orange);}
  .pipeline-columns{display:flex;gap:1px;background:var(--border-color);overflow-x:auto;}
  .pipeline-col{background:var(--bg-tertiary);padding:16px 14px;min-width:170px;flex:1 0 170px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
  .stage-eyebrow{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin:0;}
  .pipeline-stage-head{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.02em;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:2px 0 4px;line-height:1.3;min-height:28px;}
  .pipeline-card{background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid transparent;overflow:hidden;}
